  <brief_title>Pain in Single Incision Laparoscopic Surgery Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Study of Different Pain Scores in Single Transumbilical Incision Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy Versus Classic Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
